overview: Lost & Found Video Night returns AGAIN with Lost & Found Video Night Vol. 15! Featuring an over abundance of SATAN, amazing movie trailers for “Abby” & the Paul Naschy classic “Assignment Terror”, the drama of Andy Kaufman being voted off of Saturday Night Live, “Mickey Goes to Vietnam”, public access prank phone calls, inside the life & mind of a Juggalo, "Perry Como Still Alive!", examples of weapons recovered from Pelican Bay State Prison on a weekly basis, music videos from Warren Zevon, Lee Hazlewood, Duran Duran, Wayne “The Train” Hancock & The Bats, a super rare Pee Wee Herman short from late night TV and SO much more material to destroy your mind! Get with it!
title: Lost & Found Video Night Vol. 15
